{
  "chapter": 174,
  "chapter_summary": "第174章《爱恨情仇》分两条主线展开。寇仲方面：刘武周麾下大将宋金刚通过云玉真引荐与寇仲会面，展现出非凡的战略眼光。宋金刚分析天下群雄态势——李密虽声势最盛但元气大伤，杜伏威手段严苛却缺乏大志，窦建德受阻于宇文化及无法南下。他透露刘武周的战略意图：趁薛举反攻长安之际，直捣李渊老巢太原。寇仲对宋金刚的判断力深为佩服，同时也意识到自己在政制方面的不足。跋锋寒方面：芭黛儿誓言要取跋锋寒首级，突利现身助阵，但芭黛儿拒绝突利在场后离去。跋锋寒与突利展开激战，双方实力旗鼓相当。就在胜负未分之际，李渊之弟李神通突然现身，欲与突利联手对付跋锋寒。突利却出人意料地宣布停手，令局势更加扑朔迷离。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "speaker_name": "宋金刚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "定扬可汗麾下先锋将宋金刚，拜见寇兄。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "text": "我听过始毕可汗、处罗可汗、颉利可汗，甚或刚来洛阳的突利可汗，偏是没听过定扬可汗，宋兄不是改了个汉名的突厥人吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "speaker_name": "宋金刚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇兄误会了！敝主刘武周，只是受突厥人封为可汗，却非是突厥人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "在这里淋雨，不若到屋内细谈吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_dai_er",
      "speaker_name": "芭黛儿",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "当我行囊内放有你的头颅之日，就是我回去之时。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_ba_dai_er",
      "text": "黛儿回去吧！这是个不适合你的地方，芭黛儿只属于积雪山峰下的大草原。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_tu_li",
      "text": "突利你不敢现身吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_li",
      "speaker_name": "突利",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "区区一个马贼，竟能使我们劳师动众，跋锋寒你也足以自豪。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_tu_li",
      "text": "我们之所以成为小马贼，皆拜你们这群大马贼的恩赐。强者为王，此乃千古不易的真理。如今就让跋某人领教你的伏鹰枪法，好完成上趟我们未竟之战。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_li",
      "speaker_name": "突利",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "死到临头，仍敢口出狂言。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_li",
      "speaker_name": "突利",
      "listener": "char_ba_dai_er",
      "text": "黛儿你不是为这一天苦候多年吗？现在我便为你押阵，让你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_dai_er",
      "speaker_name": "芭黛儿",
      "listener": "char_tu_li",
      "text": "你曾答应我不会来的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_li",
      "speaker_name": "突利",
      "listener": "char_ba_dai_er",
      "text": "我是关心你嘛！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_dai_er",
      "speaker_name": "芭黛儿",
      "listener": "char_tu_li",
      "text": "有你在场，我绝不会动手。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "speaker_name": "宋金刚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇兄不愧当今英雄人物，只耍几下手段，便使北方的形势顿时改观，至此方知江湖上对寇兄的赞语，非是夸大之言。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "text": "只是因缘巧合下，使寇某适逢其会吧了。宋兄是否有要事相询？何不直言。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "卜天志",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇爷的词锋愈来愈厉害哩！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "speaker_name": "宋金刚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "在洽商要事之前，请容在下探问一句，寇兄与王世充是何关系。寇兄请恕在下冒昧直言。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "text": "你真够坦白，连我都弄不清楚和王世充是甚么关系？怕该是'互相利用'而已。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "王世充是头老狐狸，你这头小狐狸小心给人吃掉。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "speaker_name": "宋金刚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "和寇兄说话确是痛快之至，我亦不想再兜圈子，现今天下群雄中，论声势自要数战无不胜的李密为首，但论实力则以窦建德和杜伏威不相上下，寇兄是否同意在下作此谬论。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "text": "李密刚大胜宇文化及的十万精兵，何以实力却落于窦建德和杜伏威之后？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "speaker_name": "宋金刚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "看寇兄的神情，便知他最消楚其中情况，不如由寇兄说吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "text": "道理非常简单，只从王世充敢以二万兵力进驻偃师，摆出兵胁虎牢的高姿态，便可推知李密虽胜宇文化及，却是元气大伤的惨胜。不过老杜攻竟陵时亦是损兵折将，何以仍能与窦建德相提并论？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "speaker_name": "宋金刚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "李密和杜伏威的分别，在于一个要收买人心，另一个则只求胜利不择手段。故前者采行募兵制，而后者则从一开始便强徵平民入伍。因此杜伏威每能在短时间内补足兵源，只要兵器粮马各方面应付得来便成。此法的弊处是兵卒杂而不精，士气散漫。但在杜伏威严苛的手段压制下，在一般的情况下是不会出乱子的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "speaker_name": "宋金刚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "杜伏威声势虽盛，照我看却是个没有大志的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "卜天志",
      "listener": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "text": "宋将军何以有此看法？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "speaker_name": "宋金刚",
      "listener": "char_bu_tian_zhi",
      "text": "有大志者，眼光岂会如此短浅，只顾目前之利。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "text": "那李密该算有大志的人了，只看他收买人心的手段便可见一二。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "speaker_name": "宋金刚",
      "listener": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "text": "李密确是心怀壮志的人，只是心胸过于狭窄，有一翟让而不能容；又下蒲山公令追杀寇兄和徐兄，结果偷鸡不成反蚀把米，声威受损不在话下，最大弊处是反而树立两个劲敌。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "text": "那么贵上，嘿！甚么可汗的该是最有大志的人了！但投靠突厥，岂是长远之策？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "speaker_name": "宋金刚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "即使李渊据守关中，也要向突厥称臣，何况我们邻靠突厥，此乃权宜之计，别无选择。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "speaker_name": "宋金刚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "据我所知，李世民的上策院正着意修改隋朝旧法，新定的税制名为租庸调法，大概是每丁租二石、绢两疋、绵三两、役二十日，不役着每日折绢三尺，简单易行，一去前朝弊政，这就叫志向远大，非只是着眼目前。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "text": "宋兄仍未说出今趟找我寇仲，究竟是为了甚么事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "speaker_name": "宋金刚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇兄是否想收复竟陵呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "text": "当然想得要命。但一来手上尚有几件更迫切的大事要做，而形势更不容许，我只好等他娘的一段日子才想这个问题。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "speaker_name": "宋金刚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "兵家争战，刻不容缓，岂能久候。现在形势清楚分明，李密与王世充决战在即，不论谁胜谁负，都免不了大伤元气。在这情况下，只要杜伏威破李子通取得江都，便会循宇文化及的旧路沿运河北上。而唯一不同之处，由于杜伏威有整个江淮作后援，不虞有粮食不继之患，那时天下谁还能与江淮劲旅争锋？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "text": "你好像漏说了关中李家和夏王窦建德哩！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "speaker_name": "宋金刚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "新秦霸王薛举上趟被李世民所败，痛定思变，正密锣紧鼓准备大举反攻，那时李渊自顾不暇，那有能力兼营关外，只能坐看杜伏威耀武扬威。至于窦建德嘛，一天破不了宇文化及和徐圆朗，亦不敢轻率南下，何时才轮到他兵迫东都。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "text": "薛举若攻打长安，宋兄有甚么大计呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "speaker_name": "宋金刚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我们自然要直捣李渊的老巢，断他的根本。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "text": "太原！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "卜天志",
      "listener": "char_song_jin_gang",
      "text": "太原！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_li",
      "speaker_name": "突利",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "害怕了吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_tu_li",
      "text": "你突利万水千山的来到这里，难道就是那么的隔远舞枪弄棒？说出来也要笑死人。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_li",
      "speaker_name": "突利",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "跋锋寒你非是外行人，却偏说出这种外行话，谁才可笑？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shen_tong",
      "speaker_name": "李神通",
      "listener": "char_tu_li",
      "text": "可汗的破剑枪法果然不同凡响，该是胜券在握，不过为了省点时间，何不让我李神通也作个陪客，收拾了这小贼后大家携手喝酒，不是更痛快吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_li",
      "speaker_name": "突利",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "要喝酒还不容易，今天不打哩！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 174,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    }
  ],
